  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peru partner learning exchange and training on accountability, complaints and safeguarding</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to provide the foundation for all 10 Peru partners to work on accountability, put in place feedback and complaints mechanisms and draft codes of conduct. Partners that have already developed these mechanisms will share their experiences of doing so. This will also enable a three-day workshop in June 2019 to be held with two prioritised partners (IDECA and DHSF) to develop their own safeguarding policies, through participatory training with Warmi Huasi acting as a consultant.</narrative>
  </description>
